metatags.og:description: After the US military shot down unidentified aerial objects in North American airspace, social media users claimed that a video showed another object flying over the United States and Canada, with some calling it a UFO. But the heavily viewed footage is misleading and old; it was filmed in September 2020 from a highway in the state of New Jersey and shows a Goodyear blimp after it flew over an American football stadium.
